1498754209.text: "Our results showed that GEN-27 increased expressions of adenomatous polyposis coli (APC) and axis inhibition protein 2 (AXIN2), and reduced beta-catenin nuclear localization, which resulted from the inhibition of NF-kappaB and p65 nuclear localization and up-regulation of caudal related homeobox transcription factor 2 (CDX2)."
